reviews.text: Very authentic restaurant. I would recommend visiting it over lunch time to get seated on a table with locals. We had different dishes some were tasty, some hard to describe. Overall a nice experience and friendly staff. Although master and visa labels are on the entrance, you can only pay cash.

Hard to find spot. Food is good, nothing amazing.  Dim sum is hot and fresh.  It's the unique and busy tea house atmosphere that is interesting. Tables are shared unless you have a few people to fill the seats at the table. Still enjoyed having a quick bite.

This place is just a unique experience, you feel going back in time. Nothing seems to have changed there for decades. It's victim of its popularity though, when we got there the place was packed but it really contributes to the authentic vibes of the place ! You just go and pick any dim sum that looks good to you. Be quick as you have to follow waiters to grab it ! It's like a dim sum treasure hunt. Lot of choice and quality is fine for the price. We sat with locals and ate with them and had a great time there. Go there at least once, it's worth the stop.

One of the oldest tea house in central . Expect to be crowded and share your tables with others. Piping hot dim sum and traditional evening meals are to be had. The place is not that clean so do not expect 5 star service!
We went around 3pm and most of the dim sum were sold out. Not so clean and staffs seemed like they didn’t care at all. Dim dim sum is way much better.

reviews.text: 招呼和員工態度都比中上環好🤞🤞
我也是看了網路上的推薦才來的，不知道是不是跑錯家了，點心品項少的可憐，金錢雞的雞肝有味道 肉有騷味顯然是不新鮮，而鴨腳包可能是我的牙口不好 竟然咬不動，燒賣爛兮兮 蝦餃皮蠻韌的，燒鵝也偏乾，感覺蠻失望的
同囡囡試舊式飲茶用具,不用茶壺轉用茶蛊。哈哈哈...起初囡不懂用加水倒都滿枱都是水😂,慢慢掌握了。價錢都略貴,茶錢每位要$13。

reviews.author_name: Love Life 香港!ブログ編集部
reviews.text:
中環（セントラル）の老舗飲茶レストラン「蓮香樓」が2019年に立ち退きに迫られ、姉妹店として2018年に荃灣（チュンワン）エリアにオープンしたのがこちらのお店。

古き良きワゴンスタイルで、できたての点心がどんどん運ばれて来ます。程よい喧騒と、点心の湯気が立ち上るシーンはぜひ味わって欲しいところ。

パンダホテルから徒歩10分なので、パンダホテルにお泊まりの際は是非どうぞ。
無錯經營手法好過老蓮香，素來最憎有人企响身邊等位，根本影響飲茶情緒，所以這裡沒有上述情況，食物直係純粹普普通通，要求不高可以光顧！
